        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " do significantly better dropping out. And the kid who comes from money might someday see that money run out (perhaps as a result of a global pandemic). ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "What’s he going to do with all that college debt then?",
